Here's my new graph.

```{r}

library(dplyr)
library(readr)
library(ggplot2)
```

```{r}
#| code-fold: true
#| message: false
mtcars %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = cyl, y= hp))+
  geom_smooth(method=lm)+
  labs(x = 'Number of Cyliders', y = 'Horsepower')
```
```{r}
hp_cyl <- lm(hp ~ cyl,data=mtcars)
summary(hp_cyl)
```
